<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FnCowQo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFnCowQo.png&h=99eba852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GDruDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GDruDz.png&h=1d633373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UszDwT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UszDwT.png&h=135a5e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXwQbQD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXwQbQD.png&h=66b45ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下巴帶裝好少少唔好太求其扭埋一堆，長短set返唔好太鬆太緊，如果唔係會唔舒服。<br />\n其實一般會跟說明書，唔肯定裝得啱唔啱可以睇睇。<br />\n有啲高級啲仲可以配埋面罩，耳罩，透明鏡片，太陽擋，防曬布等，不過相對又貴啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsor，個教學有啲阿媽係女人咁廢，不過安全真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2f63ae54828042bdcac69db0dcad6951fdad60","tid":1329727,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:16:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0cc48589c104a37e420f30708bbe12876511f669","tid":1329727,"uid":207217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"eb538369f2eb3b64b0808322ea77b11c7f241258","tid":1329727,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"65cb120aab43c5e575e592e3e32b9fb6b0834bef","tid":1329727,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"職安真漢子<br />\n工友們出入工地要做足安全措施, 齊齊整整放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be030af5cbd85d818483af37c77eb3be7e6b4b9b","tid":1329727,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e83301f500d66f5f350a006883c8711b4e098d9","tid":1329727,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe300e64ab29ed64601b05163e263f1c5a9c9076","tid":1329727,"u